using easyocr: https://github.com/JaidedAI/EasyOCR?tab=readme-ov-file&fbclid=IwAR184oyq5hqCfvKqFOQe4AH6Lcepw0uoZElnPIrwmp-2P5DrimuDP8Z1GMk#api-documentation

using kafka:
• Download Kafka (Binary) from https://kafka.apache.org/

• Unzip the download file move it to C:\ drive

Run the following command to start ZooKeeper(terminal 1):
cd C:\kafka_2.12-3.6.0
bin\windows\zookeeper-server-start.bat config\zookeeper.properties


Start the Kafka cluster
• Run the following command to start the Kafka broker(terminal 2):
cd C:\kafka_2.12-3.6.0
bin\windows\kafka-server-start.bat config\server.properties

TO RUN:
1. keep running 2 terminal and run camera.py
2. run handle.py
